description:
Generates a temporary 5-digit code that can be used for elevation.

A manager generates this code on their own device, and can then manually copy this code on the user's device when requested.

:shield: Requires `Security:ElevatedFunctionalityProvider` to contain "TemporaryElevationCode".

:point_right: Send this temporary code as elevation header with your original call.

:bulb: Note it's only valid for a limited period of time (as per `Security:TemporaryElevationCode:ExpireInMinutes`) and is a /separate/ code from your login PIN!
